<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Motivation for Students</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .quote {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #333;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .author {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: -10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #aaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Keep Pushing Forward</h1>
        <p>Dear Student,</p>
        <p>
            Your recent results may not have been what you hoped for, but remember that they do not define your worth or potential. Every setback is an opportunity to learn, grow, and come back stronger.
        </p>
        <p class="quote">"Success is not final, failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts."</p>
        <p class="author">- Winston S. Churchill</p>
        <p>
            Believe in yourself, keep working hard, and never give up on your dreams. Great things take time, and with perseverance, you can achieve anything you set your mind to.
        </p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best Wishes,</p>
            <p>God Bless You</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
